SimpleProducer(n p);i;config;producer;err
‚çù A producer produces n+1 msgs on a single topic.
‚çù The partitioner assign partitions
‚çù depending on the key value (p is number of keys)
:If n<1
    ‚éï‚Üê'Please produce at least one message.'
    :Return
:EndIf

:If p<1
    ‚éï‚Üê'Minimum number of key required is 1.'
    :Return
:EndIf

#.Init '.'

‚çù Producer configurations
config‚Üê0 2‚ç¥‚ç¨
config‚ç™‚Üê'bootstrap.servers' 'localhost:9092'
config‚ç™‚Üê'client.id' 'producerclient'
‚éï‚Üê'Producer configuration'
config

‚çù Init new Producer
producer‚Üê‚éïNEW #.Producer config

‚çù Produce messages on topic
‚éï‚Üê'Produce a message on topic: topic'
producer.produce 'topic' 'payload0' 'key0'

‚éï‚Üê'Produce messages on topic: topic'
‚çù Produce n bundled messages on topic topic1 and ask for dr
:For i :In ‚ç≥n
  producer.produce_record ‚éïNEW #.Record('topic'('payload',‚çïi) ('key',‚çïp|i-1))
     :If 0=10|i
         ‚éï‚Üê'Delivery report:'
         producer.update_outstanding
     :EndIf
 :EndFor

‚éïEX 'producer'
